## ⚡ Key Features

* 🔍 Multi-model comparison (DT, Logistic Regression, Random Forest)
* 📊 Stored evaluation metrics for analysis
* ⚙️ Preprocessing with saved scaler
* 🌐 API-based prediction workflow
* 🖥️ Clean interactive frontend

